# Media Asset Dashboard - Design System Rules

You are an expert in React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, Radix UI, and modern frontend development. This project is a Media Asset Dashboard with a strict design system.

## Project Context
- **Framework:** React 19 with TypeScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 (utility-first)
- **Components:** Radix UI primitives + CVA (Class Variance Authority)
- **Icons:** Lucide React
- **Theme:** Dark-first design

## Design System - MUST FOLLOW

### Color Palette (Use these EXACT values)
```
Background Colors:
- Neutral/900: #010101 (main background, sidebars)
- Neutral/800: #181818 (cards, panels, content areas)
- Neutral/700: #282828 (buttons, inputs, interactive elements)
- Neutral/600: #333333 (borders, dividers, hover states)
- Neutral/500: #404040 (selected states)
- Neutral/400: #5D5D5D (badge backgrounds)

Text Colors:
- Neutral/100: #F0F0F0 (primary text)
- Neutral/200: #BABABA (secondary text, placeholders)
- Neutral/0: #FFFFFF (high emphasis text)

Accent Colors:
- Primary: #E5FF00 (lime-yellow - active states, selections)
- Secondary: #80B8FF (light blue - links)
```

### Typography Scale
```
H1: 24px, font-weight: 600, line-height: 1.5, letter-spacing: -0.3125px
H2: 18px, font-weight: 600, line-height: 1.5, letter-spacing: -0.3125px
H3: 16px, font-weight: 600, line-height: 1.5, letter-spacing: -0.3125px
H4: 14px, font-weight: 600, line-height: 1.5
Body: 14px, font-weight: 400, line-height: 1.5
Small: 12px, font-weight: 400, line-height: 1.4
Label: 11px, font-weight: 400, line-height: 1.4
```

Use Tailwind classes:
- `text-2xl font-semibold` for H1
- `text-lg font-semibold` for H2
- `text-base font-semibold` for H3
- `text-sm font-semibold` for H4
- `text-sm` for Body
- `text-xs` for Small/Label

### Spacing (8px Grid System)
```
xs: 2px (tight gaps)
sm: 4px (small gaps between badges, icons)
md: 8px (standard padding/gaps) - gap-2, p-2
lg: 16px (section gaps, sidebar padding) - gap-4, p-4
xl: 24px (large section gaps, card padding) - gap-6, p-6
```

### Border Radius
```
sm: 8px (rounded-lg) - buttons, inputs, cards, badges
md: 10px - navigation items
lg: 16px (rounded-2xl) - counter badges (pill)
xl: 24px - filter tags (pill)
full: 50% (rounded-full) - avatars, circular icons
```

### Key Dimensions
```
Elements Bar: 80px width
Category Sidebar: 271px width
Media Card: 350px width
Media Thumbnail: 349px × 196px (16:9 aspect ratio)
Button default: h-9 (36px)
Button small: h-8 (32px)
Button large: h-10 (40px)
Icon Button: 36px × 36px
```

## Component Patterns

### Always use the cn() utility for class merging
```tsx
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";

// Correct
<div className={cn("base-classes", conditionalClass, className)} />

// Wrong - never concatenate strings directly
<div className={`base-classes ${className}`} />
```

### Button Pattern (CVA)
```tsx
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";

// Use existing variants: default, destructive, outline, secondary, ghost, link
// Use existing sizes: default (h-9), sm (h-8), lg (h-10), icon
<Button variant="default" size="default">Click me</Button>
```

### Card Pattern
```tsx
import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardContent, CardAction } from "@/components/ui/card";

<Card>
  <CardHeader>
    <CardTitle>Title</CardTitle>
    <CardAction>
      <Button variant="ghost" size="icon">...</Button>
    </CardAction>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    {/* Content */}
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```

### Badge Pattern
```tsx
import { Badge } from "@/components/ui/badge";

// Variants: default, secondary, destructive, outline
<Badge variant="secondary">16:9</Badge>
```

### Icons
```tsx
import { IconName } from "lucide-react";

// Always use consistent sizing
<IconName className="h-4 w-4" />  // Small (16px)
<IconName className="h-5 w-5" />  // Medium (20px)
<IconName className="h-6 w-6" />  // Large (24px)
```

